## CKNE-Aware Per-Tenant Data Privacy and Retention Policy

### CKNE-to-Policy Mapping

| CKNE Range | Retention Window | Anonymization Level | Pruning Priority |
|-----------|------------------|--------------------|-------------------|
| 0.0 – 0.3 | 7 days | None | 3 (highest) |
| 0.3 – 0.6 | 14 days | Partial | 2 (medium) |
| 0.6 – 0.8 | 30 days | Full | 1 (low) |
| 0.8 – 1.0 | 90 days | Full + Encryption | 0 (preserve) |

**Rationale:** Low-CKNE tenants (minimal privacy exposure) receive aggressive pruning to free capacity, while high-CKNE tenants retain data longer with stronger anonymization to meet compliance requirements.

### Minute-by-Minute Pruning Scheduler

```javascript
class PruningScheduler {
  constructor(tenants, slaConfig) {
    this.tenants = tenants;
    this.slaConfig = slaConfig;
    this.minuteTick = 0;
  }

  tick() {
    this.minuteTick++;
    const eligible = this.getEligibleTenants();
    const sorted = this.sortByPriority(eligible);
    const batch = this.selectBatch(sorted);

    for (const tenant of batch) {
      if (this.withinSla()) {
        this.prune(tenant);
      }
    }
  }

  getEligibleTenants() {
    return [...this.tenants.values()].filter(t =>
      t.policy.pruningPriority > 0 &&
      (this.minuteTick - t.lastPruned) >= this.slaConfig.minIntervalMinutes
    );
  }

  sortByPriority(tenants) {
    return tenants.sort((a, b) => b.policy.pruningPriority - a.policy.pruningPriority);
  }

  selectBatch(tenants) {
    const capacity = this.slaConfig.maxPruningLoadPercent / 100;
    return tenants.slice(0, Math.floor(tenants.length * capacity));
  }

  withinSla() {
    return currentSystemLoad() < this.slaConfig.maxPruningLoadPercent;
  }

  prune(tenant) {
    executePrune(tenant.id, tenant.policy.retentionWindow);
    tenant.lastPruned = this.minuteTick;
  }
}
```

**Scheduler Logic:**
- Executes every minute via cron or event loop
- Prioritizes low-CKNE (high pruning priority) tenants first
- Caps resource consumption to preserve SLA for active queries
- Enforces minimum interval between pruning runs per tenant to avoid latency spikes

