- CKNE < 0.3: 1GB cache, 24h retention
- CKNE 0.3-0.7: 5GB cache, 72h retention
- CKNE > 0.7: 20GB cache, 7d retention

**Fairness Guarantees:**
- Minimum 1 slot per tenant
- 5-minute grace period before preemption
- Priority queue for critical builds
- Weighted round-robin for equal CKNE tenants

